---
<section id="inicio" class="relative bg-z-dark overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
        <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-z-gold/30 bg-z-gold/10 text-z-gold text-sm font-medium">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-z-gold opacity-75"></span>
                  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-z-gold"></span>
                </span>
                Arquitectura .NET - 100% Sin Internet
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl max-w-4xl">
                <span class="block">El Sistema de Punto de Venta con</span>
                <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-z-blue to-z-gold pb-2">Compatibilidad Extrema</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base text-slate-400 sm:text-lg md:text-xl">
                Evita caídas de sistema y costosas suscripciones. Una arquitectura robusta diseñada para operar a prueba de fallos desde Windows XP hasta Windows 11.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
                <a href="#contacto" class="px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-z-blue hover:bg-z-blue-dark shadow-xl shadow-z-blue/20 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Solicitar Demo Gratuita
                </a>
                <a href="#caracteristicas" class="px-8 py-4 border border-z-blue-dark text-lg font-medium rounded-lg text-z-light/80 bg-z-blue-dark/40 hover:bg-z-blue-dark hover:text-white transition-all">
                    Ver Módulos
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-z-light/50 font-medium">Pago único. La licencia es tuya de por vida.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-full overflow-hidden leading-none z-[-1] opacity-20">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-z-blue-dark to-transparent h-96 w-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
</section>